-- out/todo.txt --
v3 reports incomplete errors for reference.toWithinDefinition, toFieldFromDefinition, toNonDefinition, toConcrete sub-fields (required field missing), whereas v2 resolved those fields to concrete values. v3 also shows structure sharing (~) for reference.toFieldFromDefinition.p1.b and p2.b.
issue3918.noFunction.x: v3 evaluates x as a structure-shared reference to _foo.in (formatted as a bare identifier "in" that cannot be compiled standalone); the expected struct only asserts on #disjuncts and _foo.
